<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ðŸŒ» SunSafe</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            height: 100vh;
            background: url("../images/pngtree-background-pastel-yellow-picture-image_1589646.jpg") no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 0;
            color: #000;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #000;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        form {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 400px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Adjust the font size */
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; /* Change the font style */
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        form label {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #000;
        }

        form input {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: #333;
        }

        form button {
            padding: 15px;
            background: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
        }

        section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-size: cover;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 70px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Adjust the font size */
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; /* Change the font style */
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out; /* Add fade-in animation to table rows */
        }

        th {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .idk{
            background-image: url("../images/desktop-wallpaper-6-pastel-yellow-yellow-pastel-aesthetic-thumbnail.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .UV {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 350px;
            margin-right: 350px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Adjust the font size */
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; /* Change the font style */
        }

        .text {
            padding: 0 20px 0 90px;
        }

        .img {
            padding: 0 30px 0 30px;
            height: 600%;
        }

        .parallax {
            height: 250px;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            color: black;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Header Section with Parallax Effect -->
    <header>
        <div>
            <h1>Welcome to SunSafe</h1>
            <p>Discover the right protection for your skin!</p>
            <p>Scroll down to know your skin type</p>
            <!-- Sign-in Form -->
            <form id="locForm" method="post" action="/submit">
                <label for="skinInput">Enter your skin type:</label>
                <input type="text" id="skinInput" name="skin">
                <label for="locInput">Enter your location:</label>
                <input type="text" id="locInput" name="loc">
                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Skin Types Table Section -->

    <div class="idk">
        <section>
            <table>
                <h1>Skin Types</h1>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Skin Type</th>
                        <th>Typical Features</th>
                        <th>Tanning Ability</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>I</td>
                        <td>Pale white skin, blue/green eyes, blond/red hair</td>
                        <td>Always burns, does not tan</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>II</td>
                        <td>Fair skin, blue eyes</td>
                        <td>Burns easily, tans poorly</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>III</td>
                        <td>Darker white skin</td>
                        <td>Tans after initial burn</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>IV</td>
                        <td>Light brown skin</td>
                        <td>Burns minimally, tans easily</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>V</td>
                        <td>Brown skin</td>
                        <td>Rarely burns, tans darkly easily</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>VI</td>
                        <td>Dark brown or black skin</td>
                        <td>Never burns, always tans darkly</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>
    
        <div class="UV">
            <div class="img">
                <img src="../images/UV-Index.png" width="140%">
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h3>What is UV index?</h3>
                <p>The UV Index provides a daily forecast of the expected risk of overexposure to the sun. The Index predicts UV intensity levels on a scale of 1 to 11+, where 1 indicates a minimal risk of overexposure and 11+ means a very high risk.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Parallax Section -->
        <div class="parallax">
            <div>
                <h2>Enjoy the Sun Responsibly</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <footer>
            &copy; 2023 SunSafe
        </footer>
    
        <!-- Optional: Add a JavaScript library for smoother scrolling -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function () {
                // Smooth scrolling for anchor links
                $('a[href^="#"]').on('click', function (event) {
                    var target = $(this.getAttribute('href'));
                    if (target.length) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        $('html, body').stop().animate({
                            scrollTop: target.offset().top
                        }, 1000);
                    }
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
